"c4891f4b3063488f12ec7a180cb14c79", "title": "DHL Appoints Thomas Kipp as New Head of Strategy & Business Development for Post - eCommerce - Parcel division"}, "publication": "PRNewswire Asia", "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/juergen-gerdes/press"}], "_key": "fec9ec9001db0f44", "description": "Mr. Juergen Gerdes has been Member of the Management Board responsible for the MAIL Division at Deutsche Post AG since March 5, 2008. He was also Member of the Management Board responsible for PARCEL Germany at the Company from July 1, 2007 until March 4, 2008. In 1987, Mr. Gerdes gained a University degree in Administration with Deutsche Post and in 1994, he gained a degree in Business Administration at Westfaelische Wilhelms-Universitaet Muenster. In 1994, he joined Deutsche Bundespost POSTDIENST as Product Manager Infopost/Advertising Mail. In 1996, he became Director Product Management Infopost/Advertising Mail and Head of Staff Department Marketing at Deutsche Post AG. In 1997, Mr. Gerdes became Head of Sales and Operations Lower Saxony Region at Deutsche Post AG. In 1999, he became a Member of the Divisional Board MAIL Germany, Managing Director Central Key Account Management (Sales) at Deutsche Post AG."}
{"updated": "2017-08-15T00:27:07", "news_urls": ["https://www.crunchbase.com/person/parker-williams/press"], "name": "Parker Williams", "total_news_count": "1", "gender": "Male", "last_visited": "2017-08-15T00:27:07", "websites": [{"url": "http://www.facebook.com/XeroxCorp", "type": "facebook"}, {"url": "http://twitter.com/XeroxCorp", "type": "twitter"}, {"url": "http://www.linkedin.com/pub/parker-williams/4/509/799", "type": "linkedin"}], "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/parker-williams", "location": "Unknown", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1397630371/e8656ce21863ff8f5ca9b76c36071c45.jpg", "news": [{"date": "Jun 17, 2017", "article": {"url": "http://vancouversun.com/news/local-news/canada-150/canada-150-parker-williams-b-c-s-first-socialist-mla", "publisher": "vancouversun.com", "uuid": "3ecd9138eef442df978769e3c037fad4", "title": "Canada 150: Parker Williams, B.C.'s first socialist MLA"}, "publication": "vancouversun.com", "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/parker-williams/press"}], "_key": "3c0e0bf6d38d8a65", "description": "As Vice President of Business Development for the ACS Transportation Solutions Group, Parker Williams has over 25 years of public and private sector transportation experience. Williams is responsible for ACS/Xerox revenue synergy opportunities in North America across all lines of business including electronic toll collection, motor vehicle services, parking and safety solutions, and public transit fare collection and fleet management. He serves on the Education Task Force of the International Bridge, Tunnel and Turnpike Association and is also Vice President of Education and Chair of the Transportation Institute for the National Council for Public Private Partnerships. Williams has served as Administrator of the Maryland State Highway Administration, as well as Deputy Secretary of Administration with the Pennsylvania Department of Transportation."}
