{"primary_role": "Partner @ HPI Real Estate Services & Investments", "updated": "2017-07-09T13:37:10", "jobs": [{"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/hpi-real-estate-services-investments", "company": "HPI Real Estate Services & Investments", "is_current": "true", "title": "Partner"}], "description": "Prior to joining HPI in 2011, Stan was an accomplished executive at Trammel Crow. He was recognized as a top producer within the entire company during the years of 1992 to 1998, making it as high as second in Top Gross Production in 1994 and 1998 and a Top 10 producer during five of those years. He completed over 500 lease transactions during this time. In January 1999, Stan became President of Trammell Crow Central Texas. Stan\u2019s responsibilities ultimately included overseeing a staff of 180 people that encompassed all product lines including brokerage, development, property management, accounting, and human resources that oversaw the management and leasing portfolio of over 6 million square feet. During his tenure he developed nearly $600,000,000 in commercial projects and completed almost $400,000,000 in acquisitions and dispositions.Stan is a member of Young President\u2019s Organization Austin where he continues to pursue educational experiences and build on his international connections.", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/stan-erwin", "gender": "Male", "last_visited": "2017-07-09T13:37:10", "websites": [{"url": "https://www.linkedin.com/pub/stan-erwin/3/bb8/494", "type": "linkedin"}], "name": "Stan Erwin", "_key": "4b322dca4ec73787", "location": "Austin", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1435033524/afutopqkkwuqqnzgb2mk.png", "total_jobs_count": "1"}
