{"updated": "2017-07-11T09:40:27", "jobs": [{"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/argos-risk", "company": "Argos Risk", "is_current": "true", "title": "Director, Marketing"}], "description": "Kimberlee Karr is a strategic marketing professional with a passion for brand development and experience design. A steadfast believer in meaningful customer touch points, Kimberlee has spent her career creating congruent brands that successfully tell a company's story. In 2007, she spoke on the importance of experience design at the Minnesota Chapter of the American Marketing Association's annual conference. Simultaneously a writer, designer, marketer, and manager, she thoroughly understands how all aspects of a business affect its reputation. With an unwavering devotion to entrepreneurial driven businesses, Kimberlee has had the exceptional opportunity to hone her skills in fast-paced, agile environments. She has traveled to England, Scotland, Austria, Ukraine, and Brazil to research the cultural nuances associated with international marketing. Kimberlee holds a BA in English from the University of Wisconsin \u2013 Madison and MBA in International Business and Marketing from the University of Minnesota \u2013 Carlson School of Management.", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1397750611/88ad24cfa5077257d7a827a26654d8bd.jpg", "education_urls": ["https://www.crunchbase.com/person/kimberlee-karr/education"], "total_jobs_count": "1", "total_education_count": "2", "education": [{"organization": {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/carlson-school-of-management", "follower_count": "0", "image": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_98,w_98/v1408640560/nmpyyp0euwkzoadqox9s.png", "name": "Carlson School of Management", "uuid": "4c4c210b0f8733c3e873b6f03abab264"}, "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/kimberlee-karr/education"}, {"organization": {"url": "https://www