{"primary_role": "President @ The Jel Sert Company", "updated": "2017-08-26T17:38:37", "jobs": [{"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/the-jel-sert-company", "company": "The Jel Sert Company", "is_current": "true", "period": "1997 - Current (over 20 years)", "title": "President"}], "description": "Ken Wegner, President of the Jel Sert Company and father of a childhood cancer survivor. Wegner is the grandson of Jel Sert founders Charles and Lillian Wegner, and has worked at Jel Sert since 1985, first as Director of Purchasing and then as President since 1997, although he notes that his employment at Jel Sert really began right from childhood, when he and other children in the family would help suggest, and test, new products and flavors! A graduate of Denison University in Granville, Ohio, Wegner has a long and noted history of charitable and philanthropic endeavors, including serving as Chairman of the Elmhurst Memorial Hospital Foundation Board, a board member at the Max McGraw Wildlife Foundation, and membership in WPO \u2013 Chicago.", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/ken-wegner", "gender": "Male", "last_visited": "2017-08-26T17:38:37", "name": "Ken Wegner", "_key": "358d80e4697d935c", "investments_urls": ["https://www.crunchbase.com/person/ken-wegner/investments"], "total_jobs_count": "1", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1473418943/l6gxqpanfgqcriwtlwb2.png", "total_investments_count": "1", "investments": [{"lead": false, "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/ken-wegner/investments", "amount": "$1M", "details": "Personal Investment", "date": "Oct, 2009", "type": "Series A", "invested_in": {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/geekchicdaily", "follower_count": "2", "image": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_98,w_98/v1397193062/e2b59b5acb330be14d20de3ea8c57f93.jpg", "name": "GeekChicDaily", "uuid": "4b36891589d483721218cc135a560a