{"updated": "2017-08-10T17:56:29", "jobs": [{"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/reescapital", "company": "Rees Capital", "is_current": "true", "title": "Partner"}, {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/mediconnect-global", "company": "MediConnect Global (MCG)", "is_current": "true", "title": "Executive Vice President"}], "description": "As a Partner in REES Capital, Adam Casto is dedicated to providing entrepreneurs and business owners with mentoring and advisory services to help their companies achieve improved growth and profitability. Adam is a brilliant business development executive known for his intelligence, drive, and integrity. Adam offers clients expertise in sales team development, channel management, brand strategy, market positioning, and industry and customer relationship building and retention. Prior to joining REES Capital, Adam Casto spent eight years as the Executive Vice President of Business Development for MediConnect Global, Inc. During his tenure leading the company\u2019s sales efforts, Adam successfully signed four of the five largest health payers in the United States, and his team brought on more than 10,000 user accounts across five different industry verticals - 1,300 of them in 2011 alone. Adam was a key member of the senior executive team that achieved over 1,500 percent revenue growth for MediConnect, which led to its acquisition in March 2012. For his efforts, Adam was awarded Utah Business magazine\u2019s Sales and Marketer of the Year (SAMY) award in 2012.", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1397189012/4444e7a8e1556fb9e7e7dd8bdc47d3a7.jpg", "education_urls": ["https://www.crunchbase.com/person/adam-casto/education"], "total_jobs_count": "2", "total_education_count": "2", "education": [{"organization": {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/weber-state-university", "follower_count": "1", "image": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.