{"primary_role": "Director of Revenue Optimization @ Travel Tripper", "updated": "2017-08-08T05:47:11", "jobs": [{"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/travel-tripper", "company": "Travel Tripper", "is_current": "true", "period": "2011 - Current (over 6 years)", "title": "Director of Revenue Optimization"}], "description": "Joan Lee is the Director of Revenue Optimization and heads the Client Services team at Travel Tripper. She started at Travel Tripper in 2011, built the current team from the ground up, and implemented new operating standards and processes for Travel Tripper\u2019s growing list of products and services. Her team is composed of Client Services managers, GDS analysts, and online marketing specialists in the Americas and Asia Pacific. Joan plays a vital role in the growth and development of the Client Services team in order to ensure client expectations are exceeded. Joan and her team now manage over 400 hotels globally. Specializing in hotel revenue management, Joan guides her clients to achieve maximum direct bookings from their website and efficiently manage hotels\u2019 distribution channels. She brings her experience in hotel e-commerce to help clients shift share from OTAs to direct bookings\u2014her most recent success story saw one New York client shift more than 50% of its reservations to the hotel website in 2014. Joan also contributes to the product management team. Her knowledge and experience in the hotel industry is a factor in the product life cycle, especially focusing on client usability and gathering requirements. Before Travel Tripper, Joan worked at Hilton and Starwood hotels, where she gained invaluable hotel operations and revenue management experience in multiple markets across the U.S. Joan received her Masters in Hospitality & Tourism Management and a B.S. in Economics from the University of New Orleans, and is currently working towards her marketing certification. Her passion for travel matches her tenacity and commitment to her work at Travel Tripper. When she\u2019s not working, she\u2019s most interested in cooking, volunteering, and of course traveling whenever and wherever possible.", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/joan-evelyn-lee", "gender": "Female", "last_visited": "2017-08-08T05:47:11", "name": "Joan Evelyn Lee", "_key": "522e1f1761bbe924", "total_jobs_count": "1", "images": "/assets/default_image_cb-e2471225359df18a02957cad1c97c684.png", "location": "New York"}
