tts Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals, and the National Association for the Advancement of Humane Education. She was the executive director of the Bosack and Kruger Charitable Foundation, which supports scientific education and animal welfare, from 2000 to 2008 and was a lecturer and mentor at the Center for Animals and Public Policy at Tufts University School of Veterinary Medicine from 1998 to 2013. She currently serves on the board of directors or advisors for the North American Friends of Chawton House Library, the Maine Philanthropy Center and the Humane Research Council. She graduated cum laude with a bachelor of science in English Education from the University of Missouri in Columbia, MO and has a Master of Arts in Teaching from Connecticut College in New London, CT.", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1428756141/bwrol0worjvszhxpn8oy.jpg", "education_urls": ["https://www.crunchbase.com/person/kathleen-savesky/education"], "total_jobs_count": "5", "total_education_count": "2", "education": [{"organization": {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/connecticut-college", "follower_count": "0", "image": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/fetch/s--wxjqeRNU--/c_pad,h_98,w_98/http://www.campusexplorer.com/media/125x94/Connecticut-College-2A928021.jpg", "name": "Connecticut College", "uuid": "d954acb4161ab7b31f467ed2aa7d641a"}, "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/kathleen-savesky/education", "title": "MA, Teaching"}, {"organization": {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/university-of-missouri-columbia-2", "follower_count": "1", "image": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_98,w_98/v1457420476/n6spgtpjld84xux5zgju.jpg", "name": "University of Missouri, Columbia", "uuid": "f2f5edcabe2045cd14a39b297ad8e0a3"}, "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/kathleen-savesky/education", "title": "BS, English"}], 