{"updated": "2017-08-13T17:35:21", "jobs": [{"title": "EVP Human Resources", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/accolade", "company": "Accolade", "started_on": "2012", "ended_on": "2014", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "VP of HR", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/the-hartford", "company": "The Hartford", "started_on": "2005", "ended_on": "2012", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "HR Manager", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/american-international-group", "company": "American International Group", "started_on": "2002", "ended_on": "2005", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Director of Training", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/delta-t-group", "company": "Delta-T Group", "started_on": "2000", "ended_on": "2000", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Various", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/wawa-inc", "company": "Wawa Inc", "started_on": "1993", "ended_on": "1997", "is_current": "false"}], "description": "Since joining Accolade in 2012 to lead Human Resources, Mary Creedon has helped us practice what we preach by improving our work environment for our own health and wellbeing. She's also established a scalable recruiting model to double the size of our company in 12 months. Under her direction, we've overhauled our approach to learning and have advanced our employee relations, talent management, organizational design, compensation and benefits practices. Mary has 20 years of HR leadership experience in financial services, retail, hospitality and behavioral health industries. Before joining Accolade, she served as VP of Talent Management at The Hartford Financial Services Group, where she led their Employee Relations organization and the Early Career Talent Initiative geared to 10,000 professionals. Before her seven years at Hartford, Mary served as human resources manager for American International Group Inc. and human resources director for VisionQuest National Ltd. Earlier in her career, she managed HR policies and procedures for Allied Irish Banks Plc. and also was human resource manager for Fitzpatrick Hotel Group, Cork, Ireland. She completed an MBA rotational leadership development program at Wawa Inc. Mary holds a bachelor\u2019s degree in economics with a minor in sociology from National University of Ireland and an MBA in Management from Saint Joseph\u2019s University. She also holds a JD from Widener University School of Law. A licensed attorney admitted to the Pennsylvania and New Jersey Bar, she is a member of The American Bar Association, Association of Corporate Counsel, The Society of Human Resource Managers, and The Irish Institute of Personnel Development. Mary and her husband, Bill, have two young children: Mms and Liam.", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1397182899/2de3677c17860a75583b6fb331c3a8f1.jpg", "education_urls": ["https://www.crunchbase.com/person/mary-creedon/education"], "total_jobs_count": "5", "total_education_count": "3", "education": [{"organization": {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/widener-university-school-of-law", "follower_count": "0", "name": "Widener University School of Law", "uuid": "8841c6b405d9f7b0ac4eba79a01a1215"}, "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/mary-creedon/education", "period": "2004", "title": "JD, Law"}, {"organization": {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/saint-josephs-university", "follower_count": "0", "image": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_98,w_98/v1429856788/redmxbp8ikit6skvji0h.png", "name": "Saint Joseph\u2019s University", "uuid": "dd09139b360b6eb7b2f5825c8b53020b"}, "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/mary-creedon/education", "period": "1995", "title": "MBA, Business"}, {"organization": {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/university-college-cork", "follower_count": "0", "image": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.c