{"primary_role": "CEO @ Altisource Asset Management", "updated": "2017-07-09T05:19:36", "jobs": [{"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/altisource-residential-corporation", "company": "Altisource Residential Corporation", "is_current": "true", "title": "CEO"}, {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/altisource-asset-management", "company": "Altisource Asset Management", "is_current": "true", "title": "CEO"}], "description": "Mr. Pandey has served as a Director and the Chief Executive Officer of AAMC since December 2012. He is responsible for the overall strategic direction of the Company. Prior to joining us, Mr. Pandey served as the Chief Executive Officer of Correspondent One, an affiliate of Altisource engaged in the acquisition and secondary marketing of government loans. He previously served as Executive Vice President of Ocwen from July 2008 to August 2011 and was responsible for the oversight of asset management vehicles and capital deployment for mortgage servicing portfolio acquisitions for Ocwen. He served as Treasurer and Director of Corporate Strategy from February 2005 to July 2008 for Ocwen. From May 2002 to October 2003, Mr. Pandey served as an Associate Consultant with Tata Strategic Management Group. He holds a Bachelor\u2019s of Science in Engineering from the S.G.S. Institute of Technology and Science and a Masters of Business Administration from the Indian Institute of Management.", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/ashish-pandey", "gender": "Male", "last_visited": "2017-07-09T05:19:36", "name": "Ashish Pandey", "_key": "dcd0cce170d8621f", "total_jobs_count": "2", "images": "/assets/default_image_cb-e2471225359df18a02957cad1c97c684.png", "location": "Fredericksburg"}
{"updated": "2017-08-11T08:22:22", "name": "Vita DeMarchi", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/vita-demarchi", "gender": "Female", "last_visited": "2017-08-11T08:22:22", "websites": [{"url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/vita-demarchi-3471179/", "type": "linkedin"}], "_key": "d42f8ea77bcea8e3", "location": "Syracuse", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1494230730/ladus3kihdgbwzgktrdt.png", "description": "Ms. DeMarchi is the Managing Partner at Synapse Partners. Ms. DeMarchi has been involved in assessing environmental conditions, evaluating risk, and developing and implementing strategies to address environmental conditions at thousand of real properties, operating facilities and for corporations throughout the US. As a Risk Manager, she has provided clients with the benefit of her expertise and ability to assimilate material fact contained in reports prepared by engineering and consulting firms, forensic analytical data, regulatory and legal documents, and then develops business solutions that match the risk appetite of individual clients and partners. She has provided underwriting support for environmental insurance submittals and financial transactions. Ms. DeMarchi is a Co-Founder and Director of a 501(c)(3) not-for-profit organization - Synapse Sustainability Trust, which has fostered four environmental initiatives: Universal Brownfield Revitalization Corporation, CuseCar, EvPlugSite, and Restoration Tree Trust. Ms. DeMarchi has the honor to serve as the Chairwoman of the Board of Trustees at SUNY College of Environmental Science and Forestry."}
