{"updated": "2017-07-10T14:08:33", "jobs": [{"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/zanthion-inc", "company": "Zanthion", "is_current": "true", "period": "Jan 28, 2017 - Current (5 months)", "title": "CTO (Pending Funding)"}, {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/space-time-insight", "company": "SpaceTime Insight", "is_current": "true", "period": "Jan 1, 2015 - Current (over 2 years)", "title": "Chief Technology Officer"}, {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/basf", "company": "BASF", "is_current": "true", "period": "1995 - Current (over 22 years)", "title": "Senior Plant Manager"}, {"title": "Senior Plant Manager", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/basf-venture-capital", "company": "BASF Venture Capital", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Senior Scientist & Assistant Professor", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/northwestern-university", "company": "Northwestern University", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Vice President of Research", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/sap", "company": "SAP", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Visiting Scientist", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/massachusetts-institute-of-technology-mit", "company": "Massachusetts Institute of Technology - MIT", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Chief Technology Officer", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/saffron-technology", "company": "Saffron Technology", "started_on": "Feb, 2012", "ended_on": "Aug, 2014", "is_current": "false"}], "description": "Paul Hofmann, PhD is Chief Technology Officer at Space Time Insight. He is an Advisory Board Member to Zanthion IoT and a Computer Science Advisory Board Member at Stony Brook University. Most recently, Paul served as CTO for Saffron Technology, which is now part of Intel. He served a 2 year term as Board Member at Primal from 2012 to 2014.With more than 20 years\u2019 experience in enterprise software and services, Paul\u2019s background combines academic thought leadership with international executive leadership at global companies. Before joining Saffron in 2012 Paul was Vice President Research at SAP Labs at Palo Alto. Paul has also worked for the SAP Corporate Venturing Group. Paul joined SAP in 2001 as Director for Business Development EMEA SAP AG where he has created the Value Based Selling program.Paul was visiting scientist at Civil and Environmental Engineering Department at MIT, Cambridge, MA 2009.Prior to joining SAP, Paul was Senior Plant Manager at BASF\u2019s Global Catalysts Business Unit in Ludwigshafen, Germany. Paul has been entrenched in research as Senior Scientist and Assistant Professor at outstanding European and American Universities (Northwestern University, U.S., Technical University Munich and Darmstadt, Germany). He is an expert in computational chemistry and computer graphics (Ph.D., research and teaching in Nonlinear Quantum Dynamics and Chaos Theory), authoring numerous publications and books, including a book on SCM and environmental information systems as well as performance management and productivity of supply chains. His passion has always been AI, machine learning and semantics. In 1986 Paul programmed an associative memory system at Technical University Munich to predict chemical reactions in mass spectrometer. His team at SAP Labs implemented semantic rules engine from CMU to show the right data to the right person when accessing enterprise systems, and transferred computational logic from Stanford AI Lab into the SAP Business by Design Configurator.", "total_jobs_count": "8", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1408610629/ocnfbk6fvzsyigy2nhxp.png", "news": [{"date": "May 29, 2015", "article": {"url": "http://www.prweb.com/re