{"updated": "2017-08-11T21:37:28", "jobs": [{"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/trinity-pharma-solutions", "company": "SHYFT", "is_current": "true", "title": "CEO & Founder"}, {"title": "Software Engineer", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/ef-education-first", "company": "EF Education First", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Technical Architect", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/zefer-inc", "company": "ZEFER,Inc", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}], "description": "Zack is an experienced tech executive, entrepreneur, and engineer for high-growth companies in Europe and the U.S. He is a founder of Trinity Pharma Solutions, a big data, analytics and mobile solutions company. Trinity delivers cloud-based solutions that are reinventing the way life science companies leverage data and analytics to drive commercial insights. Prior to founding Trinity, Zack was an early employee at ZEFER, a software services firm that closed $160M in venture funding and grew to over $100M in revenue, 800 people, and six global offices. Prior to Zefer, he lead engineering teams at EF Education First, the world\u2019s largest private education company.Zack is a frequent contributor to industry trade publications in healthcare and technology and an active advisor and investor to a number of early-stage technology companies. During the Gulf War, Zack served in the United States Army with the 101st Airborne Division and was awarded the elite Air Assault Badge and the Army Commendation Medal for heroism, meritorious achievement and service.Specialties: leadership, technology, pharmaceuticals, biotech, healthcare, startups, mobile, analytics, big data", "total_boards_and_advisor_roles_count": "1", "total_jobs_count": "3", "boards_and_advisor_roles_urls": ["https://www.crunchbase.com/person/zackary-king/advisory-roles"], "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.clou