{"updated": "2017-08-12T12:45:37", "jobs": [{"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/bunim-murray-productions", "company": "Bunim Murray Productions", "is_current": "true", "title": "Chief Digital Officer"}, {"title": "SVP, Digital Media and Interactive Entertainment", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/gsn", "company": "GSN", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Team Member", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/fox-broadcasting-company-2", "company": "Fox Broadcasting Company", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Team Member", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/vulcan-llc", "company": "Vulcan", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "SVP, Digital Media & Commercial Ventures USA", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/endemol", "company": "Endemol", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Senior Vice President of Digital Content & Cross-Platform Entertainment", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/the-hub", "company": "The Hub", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Team Member", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/universal-pictures", "company": "Universal Pictures", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}, {"title": "Head of Digital Media", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/lucasfilm", "company": "Lucasfilm", "started_on": "Unknown", "ended_on": "Unknown", "is_current": "false"}], "description": "John P. Roberts is a television and digital media veteran with a 20-year history of developing new business strategies, content and revenue streams for the entertainment industry. He is currently the Chief Digital Officer for Bunim-Murray Productions, a Banijay Group company. In this role, Roberts leads BMP Digital with a focus on increasing the company\u2019s digital productions, including multi-platform and digital programming for the web, mobile devices and other online and connected device distribution platforms. He will also explore digital business and investment opportunities that will drive BMP forward in the marketplace. Roberts was most recently the Senior Vice President of Digital Media and Commercial Ventures for Endemol, the world\u2019s largest independent production company. In this position, he was responsible for developing new digital and commercial business opportunities in North America. He oversaw the launches of all original digital productions, interactive television, social games and mobile apps. Prior to Endemol, Roberts served as Senior Vice President of Digital Content and Cross-Platform Entertainment at The Hub, a multi-platform joint venture between Discovery Communications and Hasbro. In that role, he was in charge of the development and execution of the network's overall digital strategy, online content, and all social media platforms. Roberts\u2019s extensive media industry knowledge stems from his work with numerous companies including Lucasfilm LTD, GSN, Vulcan Programming, Universal Studios, and News Corp. At News Corp he established Fox's first ever Internet presence Fox.com, which encompassed Fox Entertainment, Fox Sports, and Fox Kids Network. He was also on the launch team of Fox\u2019s first cable network, FX. He is a frequent speaker on industry panels such as Digital Hollywood, Banff Media Festival, Academy of Television Arts & Sciences, Producers Guild, Next TV Summit and many others. Roberts is a four-time Emmy Award nominee in interactive television and recipient of the ITV Leadership Award from ITVT.", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/john-p-roberts", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1422961949/hcueiif5phextolo9frh.png", "news": [{"date": "Jun 23, 2017", "article": {"url": "https