{"primary_role": "Project Manager @ Krediti", "updated": "2017-08-19T19:15:39", "jobs": [{"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/i2r", "company": "I2R", "is_current": "true", "title": "Project manager"}, {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/www-krediti-rs", "company": "Krediti", "is_current": "true", "title": "Project Manager"}], "description": "Miodrag Jokic is Project Manager at Krediti.rs and Co-founder at AdriaTalk.com along with Jadranka Stancic. Miodrag has written many articles and research papers covered in South-East Europe top media (B92, Blic, Danas, 24 sata, Slovenian National Television, krediti.rs, Ekonomist magazine, TV Vojvodina, Serbian National Television - RTS). He is former ERP consultant and former back office associate at one of the largest serbian stock broker companies - Sinteza Invest Group.", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/miodrag-jokic", "gender": "Male", "last_visited": "2017-08-19T19:15:39", "websites": [{"url": "http://www.facebook.com/adriatalk", "type": "facebook"}, {"url": "http://twitter.com/adriatalk", "type": "twitter"}], "name": "Miodrag Jokic", "born": "April 18, 1983", "location": "Unknown", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1397188461/1925a72145344752a1f3ac666cb67040.jpg", "_key": "701511c67edd0408", "total_jobs_count": "2"}
{"total_events_count": "1", "updated": "2017-07-10T09:23:56", "name": "Maxine Marcus", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/maxine-marcus", "gender": "Female", "last_visited": "2017-07-09T15:58:31", "_key": "25816cd406c9cbfb", "location": "Unknown", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1447055855/f0hjvazcwbtyq837wajz.jpg", "events_urls": ["https://www.crunchbase.com/person/maxine-marcus/events"], "events": [{"name": "SF MusicTech Summit", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/event/sf-musictech-summit-20151110", "image": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_60,w_60/v1441750362/uorcw5ma62gyu7dfjslr.png", "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/maxine-marcus/events", "role": "Speaker", "date": "Nov 10, 2015"}], "description": "Born and raised in the San Francisco Bay Area, Maxine Marcus is a singer/songwriter and performs on both guitar and piano. Her memorable vocal stylings, intonation, and catchy melodies infuse her original music which celebrate the human experience with its bright and dark shades. All told from a teenage perspective while balancing life, friends, high school and family. Teamed up with producer Dan Shea (Sony Music, Mariah Carey, J Lo, ), Maxine\u2019s forthcoming EP brings grit and soul together with deep bass and grooves, inspired by her love of diverse genres especially EDM, Alternative, Pop, and R&B. As the daughter of musicians, she has been surrounded by music and performing since recording her first song, \u201cBitter To Breath\u201d at the age of 13. In fact, the day before she was born, her mother was jumping up and down while performing on the stage of Slim\u2019s in San Francisco. The next generation is here."}
