{"updated": "2017-07-09T04:31:58", "name": "Kamran Mackey", "url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/kamran-mackey", "gender": "Male", "last_visited": "2017-07-09T04:31:58", "websites": [{"url": "http://www.facebook.com/kamranm12001", "type": "facebook"}, {"url": "http://twitter.com/mackeykamran", "type": "twitter"}], "born": "May 5, 2000", "location": "Calgary", "images": "/assets/default_image_cb-e2471225359df18a02957cad1c97c684.png", "_key": "a665ef982c59f748", "description": "Hi! I'm a Windows power user. I love Music, Nintendo, computers and all things related to technology. I love my Nintendo 3DS XL. I got some games for it during Christmas 2012 such as Crosswords Plus and Scribblenauts Unlimited. I have owned multiple video games systems in the past such as a Nintendo GameCube, Nintendo Game Boy, Nintendo DS, Nintendo DSi XL, a PlayStation One and also a PlayStation 2. I really love Pok\u00e9mon and Mario as well. I really hope to get a Xbox 360, PlayStation 3, Wii U or a PlayStation 4 in the future. Add me as a friend if you want to stay in touch! :) I really love learning new things and skills. I also really love teaching different things such as programs/web services/operating systems such as Facebook, WordPress, Windows and more! I also really love exploring new websites. :) I really love the Christmas holiday as well. It is my most absolute favorite time of the year because I always get lot's of presents! I also really love birthdays as well because I always get to have a party and get presents and stuff like that. :) I'm a very nice person too. I love meeting new friends. And did I mention that I really love teaching things?! Because I really do! :)"}
