onStep, Inc., which provided online collaboration technology to retail shoppers. He also served as Vice President of Product and Marketing for Subimo, a decision-support company that led the movement to develop consumer-friendly health-care tools. That business was sold to WebMD where he was Vice President of Marketing. In addition, he has been on the executive teams of Pictage, Trivida, and serves on advisory boards to various entrepreneurial businesses, including Growthink and NoviMedicine, Inc. David holds a bachelor\u2019s degree in economics from the University of Michigan and an MBA from Northwestern University\u2019s Kellogg School of Management.", "images": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_140,w_140/v1415766344/ksusixa8q84lvc4nwmev.jpg", "education_urls": ["https://www.crunchbase.com/person/david-shevock/education"], "total_boards_and_advisor_roles_count": "2", "total_jobs_count": "5", "boards_and_advisor_roles_urls": ["https://www.crunchbase.com/person/david-shevock/advisory-roles"], "total_education_count": "2", "education": [{"organization": {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/northwestern-university", "follower_count": "6", "image": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_98,w_98/v1425080609/hb1woslo1ba1uue3grmi.png", "name": "Northwestern University", "uuid": "f23fd7982cc4426ec67013e81ba24806"}, "title": "M.B.A.", "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/david-shevock/education"}, {"organization": {"url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/university-of-michigan-ann-arbor", "follower_count": "10", "image": "https://crunchbase-production-res.cloudinary.com/image/upload/c_pad,h_98,w_98/v1415443618/fqhb7ja56zlagv8vog64.png", "name": "University of Michigan", "uuid": "ef989047b04e78e77d6da9281c0e0278"}, "title": "Bachelors, Economics", "source_url": "https://www.crunchbase.com/person/david-shevock/education"}], "primary_role": "Senior Vice President @ ConnectedHe